{"tid":1178222,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"被蒙騙多年。。。。","createTime":"2019-05-30T09:08:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T13:22:52.000Z","uid":161398,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bc8f1f02760c899a5a17e706f3f81c78f8bbece3","tid":1178222,"uid":161398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T09:08:48.000Z","msg":"呢幾年左耳成日都忽然聽嘢聽得唔清楚，<br />\n覺得自己聽力好似開始慢慢下降，<br />\n有時朋友企遠少少講嘢都會聽得唔清楚，<br />\n如果問多幾次都聽唔清，<br />\n我多數會扮聽到笑住哈哈哈帶過，<br />\n點解原來佢問緊我問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日第一次用鐵棒（唔知係咪咁叫）撩耳仔，<br />\n結果bob一聲，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n耳仔好似打通任督二脈咁，<br />\n忽然聽到世界好多既聲音，<br />\n感覺好似弱聽人士忽然聽翻嘢，<br />\n好感動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後撩撩下就撩15分鐘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6472d6a31c2dcef46475b38fb156470819ad4ab0","tid":1178222,"uid":161398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T09:10:58.000Z","msg":"強烈建議大家去試下用撩耳棒撩耳仔，我覺得之前撩方法只係將佢愈推愈入 （用開棉花棒）"},{"pid":"566a6fa7179567f11f9e2c3b4fc9f1b31b1548bd","tid":1178222,"uid":19217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6472d6a31c2dcef46475b38fb156470819ad4ab0","tid":1178222,"uid":161398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T09:10:58.000Z","msg":"強烈建議大家去試下用撩耳棒撩耳仔，我覺得之前撩方法只係將佢愈推愈入 （用開棉花棒）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T09:12:23.000Z","